My husband made full use of the gym and thought is was better than a lot of hotel gyms but I have to say that the spa wasn't really worth that much of a look.	It was convenient to include our dachsund in our plans (very much worth the extra $50 deposit to have her with us rather than kennel her) and the exceptional staff had all three of us feeling more than welcome.	We felt rather cheated - if it was indeed that much, at least let us know if the price when ordering.	It was as if we each had our own room, for the price of one.